INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('579ef13829c06', '骆驼奶将拯救敏感肌，和全宇宙', '雅莉', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579eecc276886.png', 'skin:article:tag:57319ee78836e,skin:article:tag:57319f02782b6', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579eef8c44170.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579eef7776515.png', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">美容达人Kristin是一个皮肤和头发护理魔法师，她崇尚自然美，拒绝使用有害的化学成分和动物测试。身为敏感肌肤，她也在常年探索最适合敏感肌的天然元素。今天我们就要和你一起分享她与骆驼奶的缘分！</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">为什么是骆驼奶？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">2016年开始到现在，我70%的时间大部分花在寻找骆驼奶上。在纽约布鲁克林街道上看不到成群的骆驼，也许你会说健康的食品在超市都可以买得到。但是我对喝骆驼奶不感兴趣，让我乐此不疲的是骆驼奶的护肤功效，从而可以不知疲倦的去寻找最好的奶源。感谢Desert Farms，让我找到一些最好的骆驼奶，可以开始我的DIY护肤配方。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">这不是在做PK，但骆驼奶的确含铁量比牛奶的高，还富含更多维生素C和维生素B。它不仅有天然的保湿作用，还能改善皮肤弹性。你是不是有时洗完脸后皮肤感觉轻微紧绷？但骆驼奶不会这样，因为吸收水份已经在洗脸时渗入到了你的肌肤深层。而且根据美国国家公共电台NPA的报道，骆<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">驼奶的抗体已经过测试，证明能改善痘痘，其舒缓特性能治疗皮肤发炎。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">你可以是个完全正常的人，购买一些神奇的骆驼奶皮肤护理或头发护理产品，或者成为像我一样的怪咖，奇思异想地研发出一些非常舒缓的护肤配方。通常，我喜欢DIY，所以可以为自己的皮肤私人定制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpEMDBS9\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ef0a722e8f.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">DIY和小众骆驼奶</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">在DIY前，我试用了一些Desert Farms的产品,获得些许灵感。我尝试了一款新面膜，尽管它花费了我十五分钟。在整个敷面膜过程中及清洗后，脸部皮肤都没有干燥感，而以往用其他产品却有干燥紧绷感。我现在每天都会敷骆驼奶面膜至少一次，没有任何不适感或刺激感。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">这款面膜钱花得值得。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">我之所以不用通常的肥皂洗脸是有很多原因的，最大的一个原因就是，我发现传统的肥皂配方令我的脸非常干燥，甚至那些天然皂都会让我的皮肤更容易发炎。我想敏感肌肤不只有我一个人，所以我迫不及待的分享这款骆驼奶肥皂给大家。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">骆驼奶肥皂真的非常温和，我持续使用了一周，零刺激。</span></span>亲自体验产品后我受到巨大的启发，所以我开始用Desert Farms的纯骆驼奶制作适合自己的护肤品。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1.骆驼奶洗</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">发水</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">给头发来一次牛奶浴已经很老套的洗护方法了，但如果你尝试过骆驼奶洗发水之后，奶牛们再可爱你都会甩它九条街外去。真的！我发现骆驼奶洗发水很保湿，让头发非常闪亮——我的头发是非洲圆蓬式哑光色。洗完头发后，我给头发抹上免洗护发素。一周后，我的头发仍然非常的柔软。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpl0dBPC\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ef0cf1d48b.png\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2.骆驼奶&amp;燕麦片去角质面膜</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">我之前非常喜欢用椰奶去角质配方，现在我决定换成骆驼奶配方：三分之一杯有机燕麦，3汤匙骆驼奶（你要根据燕麦来添加）进行配制；接着倒入一汤匙的柠檬酸充当面膜防腐剂，加入几片玫瑰花瓣，拌匀，敷到清洗过后湿润的脸部，保持5分钟，再用温水洗脸，最后涂抹保湿霜。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php4MGxuv\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ef0e4b2301.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">3.骆驼奶&amp;玫瑰沐浴露</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">骆驼奶的抗菌特性使骆驼奶可以充当天然清洁剂。把这个强效营养的奶与生蜂蜜混合一起，就可以给自己制作一款温和沐浴露，就这么简单。我通常用骆驼奶、玫瑰水、生蜂蜜和几滴精油混合一起，洗澡完后就可以香喷喷啦。把混合好的材料拌匀，倒入黑色密封容器就可以保存哦。我会添加柠檬酸充当防腐剂，但我觉得放冰箱保存也不错。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpWuGL8w\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ef0fc4ca42.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">4.骆驼奶&amp;肉豆蔻磨砂按摩洗面乳</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">我最喜欢的另一个配方是骆驼奶和肉豆蔻磨砂按摩洗面乳，<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">非常温和、非常简单、非常便宜</span>，这就是为什么我们喜欢DIY的原因。只需要一汤匙的肉豆蔻粉末加上少许骆驼奶，轻轻地在脸部和颈部按摩，就可以获得一次超级轻柔的去角质护理。去角质完毕后用温水洗脸，在进行后续护理。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php92dRlT\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ef114667b5.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">5. DIY骆驼奶手工皂</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">可以学习简单皂基教程，或者网购无碱液的皂基，把骆驼奶加入自制手工皂配方中。但记得要添加柠檬酸和香精进行防腐，你也可以加入一些花瓣和喜欢的精油进行私人订制。我一般会添加新鲜的薰衣草花蕾、燕麦片和骆驼奶到皂基中。</span>亲爱的奶牛们，很抱歉，我现在正式成为了一个骆驼女孩～</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php1y2KJq\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ef122cd52e.png\" title=\"\"/><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1470034232', '1470034232', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('579eeb1332bb8', '在家滚微针，美肤速速来', '雅莉', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ee90802d40.png', 'skin:article:tag:5722bc5ee0186', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579eeaf75a91a.png', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579eeaf1c4f5c.png', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">护肤狂人为了让肌肤看起来更健康美丽，什么都愿意去尝试。有些人甚至愿意尝试用</span>200<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">根针头扎自己的皮肤，只为让自己看起来更年轻。听起来怪疯狂的——微针美容，对于这些人来说即使花费千金也值得。而在海外，这一趋势逐渐从美容医院、美容院走向居家，一笔小钱就可以在家时时滚针美肤。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">滚微针是什么原理？</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">微针美容又称微创美容，是指在手持设备上装置许多小针头，刺激脸部皮肤，制造出“微创伤”。护肤原理是通过细小的针头刺激皮肤，给身体制造受伤的假象，因此身体的会迅速生产胶原蛋白，补充到受刺激部位，对受刺激部位进行修复。这些奔涌而来的胶原蛋白会</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: underline;\">使皮肤饱满、淡化疤痕和皱纹</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">好吧，原理就这样。我猜你这时应该在思虑微针美容的过程应该很痛苦吧？其实，并不痛滴。那些针头非常的细，细到无力造成疼痛。他们只是戳刺皮肤，所以更多的是产生皮肤刺激的感觉，而没有疼痛感。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">微针美容科可以在美容医院进行，但也可以在家里进行。很多热卖的微针价格不到</span>20 <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">美元。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">建议选择</span>0.5-1.5<span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">毫米长的微针</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">。太长的针会对皮肤带来损伤，而太短的又对皮肤没什么效果。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php50YbiD\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ee8b90e1f6.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">微针带来的美容效果值得滚吗？</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); text-decoration: underline;\">微针还可以促进护肤品吸收</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">。想想那么多的细小针头对皮肤“打孔”，让护肤品直接渗入大量微型管道。</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">一</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">般传统的方法，活性养分只能渗透入表皮的阻隔层（即角质层），效果并不显著（只达到约百分之零点三的成效）。为了解决这问题，科学家经过无数的研究，研制出微针美容。此美容方法法能有效提升养份的渗透能力，穿透皮肤表皮层及真皮层之细胞，效果尤其显著，是养份输送的护肤科技新突破。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">虽然打开的微型管道可以促进护肤品的吸收，但同时也为细菌打开了通道。所以在</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: underline;\">使用滚针前要清洁皮肤和滚针消毒（用酒精擦拭）</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">微针美容跟其他根治疗法一样，也有它负的一面。比如可能为新使用者带来皮肤损伤、流血或感染，尤其是不懂得微针保养的人。微针的使用就像剃须刀的使用一样，用久了会顿，会长满细菌。所以</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: underline;\">建议每月更换</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">海外畅销居家微针产品</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">想知道自己适合哪种微针吗？下面三款畅销的微针非常适合生手哟。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong>1）Stacked Skincare Mirco Roller</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">30<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">，</span>http://stackedskincare.com/<span style=\"color: windowtext;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">这款微针非常适合新手。微针长度为</span>2<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">毫米，在家使用是超安全的。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php61MQTG\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ee8d6754de.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong>2）DermaDream 0.5 mm Derma Roller</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">30<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">美元，</span><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">lafontainecosmetics.com</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">当然这款微针不是用黄金制成的，不过土豪金也蛮美的。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpxNEthf\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ee8e803b03.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong>3）Koi Beauty Skin Care Roller</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">15.50<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">美元</span>, <span style=\"color: windowtext;\">amazon.com</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">这款在亚马逊是最畅销的微针。性价比很高。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpn9JwUj\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ee8fd12b5f.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1470032659', '1470032659', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('579ebfa857a1f', '好酒精？坏酒精？皮肤怎么聪明喝一杯', '雅莉', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ebaf246c7d.png', 'skin:article:tag:57319f12e7462', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ebeff71e5d.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ebee34fa6a.jpg', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">油性皮肤的我每次买护肤品，都有导购热烈建议买含酒精成分的产品，说酒精能去油，能缩小毛孔，真有此效果吗？也有看到美女每次提起护肤品中含有酒精，如临大敌一般，“NO NO NO我不要这个，给我换一个！”酒精到底对皮肤有没有保护作用，在化妆品中又有些什么作用呢？</span><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">护肤成分中的酒精 Bad vs. Good</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span><img alt=\"/tmp/phpfB2LaX\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ebf1e5fd92.jpg\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">我们通常所说的护肤品或化妆品中的酒精是指乙醇（ethanol）。成分列表中又名为变性酒精（SD alcohol）、异丙醇（isopropyl alcohol）、变性乙醇（alcohol denat）。这些挥发性醇类酒精能使产品加快干燥，令肌肤感觉轻盈，所以适合油性皮肤的产品中经常能看到这类酒精的身影。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">上面说的几种酒精在化妆品成分表中放在前五的位置，那么这种酒精会引起皮肤刺激，对任何肤质都有害，会导致皮肤紧绷、自由基损伤、降低皮肤修复能力，使皮肤长期处于压力状态。酒精作为护肤品的主要成分是值得我们畏惧的，但不做为主要成分也不是我们想象的那么可怕。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">还有一类名为脂肪醇fatty alcohols的酒精，对皮肤完全没有刺激，例如&nbsp;鲸蜡醇cetyl alcohol，硬脂醇stearyl alcohol，鲸蜡硬脂醇cetearyl alcohol。<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">这些成分对干性肌肤有益，如果是少量的话，也适合任何肌肤</span>。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">但是！很有必要学会识别有益酒精与有害酒精。</span><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">也许后你会好奇：如果变性酒精类对皮肤有害，为什么好多护肤品公司还使用呢？原因是：<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">这些酒精可以保持配方的稳定性或是使厚重的配方用起来更加轻盈，增加使用的愉悦感。这类酒精对产品有好处，但对皮肤无益。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">也许你也听说过酒精是个好东西的说法，因为酒精可以使维生素A和C等成分更好的渗入肌肤。尽管酒精能加强这些成分的吸收，但同时也破坏皮肤屏障。酒精坏处大于好处，其实可以采用更温和的方式使这些成分更好的渗入肌肤。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">酒精是怎样损坏皮肤+令皮肤问题更糟糕？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">酒精能迅速损坏皮肤，且在蒸发后会给皮肤带来连锁反应。2003年<em>Journal of Hospital Infection</em>曾发表过研究报告，发现经常性的使用含酒精的产品，使皮肤无法阻挡水和清洁剂的渗透，导致皮肤屏障进一步被侵蚀。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">如果你的皮肤是油性的，含酒精的产品对你会更加有吸引力，因为他们能迅速去除油光。但令人讽刺的是，用含酒精的产品去控油，最终导致皮肤更油、毛孔更粗大、炎症更严重，痘印遗留的时间更长。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">总之，酒精会激发毛孔根部油脂的产生，所以快速去油的效果最终反而令皮肤产生更多的油。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">酒精有害，又为何可以用来清理伤口？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpqbGdoh\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ebf59cf790.png\" title=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">现在，大多数医学专家都不用酒精来清理伤口，所以你不必纠结。酒精不仅具有损害性，而且对破开的皮肤也没有消毒作用。<em>Dermatology Clinics Journal</em>已经证明酒精对伤口没有消毒作用。尽管酒精有消毒作用，（这也是为什么医生打针前都会用酒精先对皮肤进行消毒），但是对破开的伤口却有害——医生一般用无菌水、生理盐水或碘进行清洗。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat repeat;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php2mpDgB\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579ebf8c71842.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat repeat;\">最后，总结：</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">1.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">干皮和敏感肌最好谨慎对待酒精。</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">不需要完全避开，而是如果它在成分表中的排名非常靠后的话这样的情况你是可以试一试，觉得没有问题，还是可以买的。但排名在前五的话就要非常慎重了。但最好不要使用含酒精的护肤品。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">2.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">对油皮的建议是，只要不是那种酒精超多的东西，都可以用，但不要长期使用。</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">油皮由于皮脂分泌旺盛，所以天生对酒精的缓冲力较强，但使用酒精后皮脂膜同时也受到损伤，所以还是遵循第一条，成分排名不要靠前，不要长时间持续大面积使用，一周一两次。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">3.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">痘痘肌或皮炎，避免使用。</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">精对破开的皮肤是没有消炎作用的，反而会进一步损伤皮肤屏障，所以为避免刺激，尽量不用含酒精的产品。如果是要进行消炎，还是用替代品吧。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1470021544', '1470021770', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('5789d4582904e', '晒伤后怎样防止皮肤脱皮？', '美肤专家娟子', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789cf15ea231.jpg', 'skin:article:tag:5727fef89cb70', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789d0f34c833.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789d0afdd897.jpg', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">我们都知道保护皮肤很重要。涂防晒霜！坐在阴凉处！戴帽子！长期的暴露在太阳下会导致皮肤癌，还会引起皱纹。那短时间暴晒又会怎么样呢？皮肤晒伤、灼痛。不仅疼痛，还会引起皮肤红肿——夏天的魅力可不是这个哦，哈哈。晒伤后还会引起皮肤脱皮，真的很恐怖，大块大块掉皮。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">当晒伤的皮肤开始脱皮时，表明身</span><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">体正在排除受损的细胞，保护皮肤不患皮肤癌，这是皮肤的自我防护方式。但问题又出来了，脱皮的地方很痒，令人很不舒服。此外，还会不断的脱皮，顶着个晒伤脱皮的额头出门，真的很影响形象。所以就不要犯这样的错误，一出现脱皮现象就要尽快护理。下面介绍7种防止晒后皮肤脱皮的方法给大家。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1.喝水</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">晒伤的皮肤非常干燥，所以最要紧的是补水，只有充分的补水才不会脱皮。先从内部补水，要多喝水，才能弥补暴晒太阳时流失<span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">的水分</span>。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpWI5aB1\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789d39f9ae2e.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2.补水</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">从内补水的同时，不要忘记外部补水。倩碧的这款晒后修复霜，蕴含芦荟，能尽量减少皮肤脱皮状况。涂抹时多抹点，豪气点。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpaIMQO7\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789d3b26bf80.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">3.家用配方</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">如果补水保湿霜还是不能完全阻止脱皮的话，试试敷牛奶、薄荷叶、苹果醋，可以减少刺痛感，以及红肿。吃燕麦或洗澡放点小苏打也可以缓解症状。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php8a8aR9\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789d4085f845.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">4.不要去角质</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">去角质会使还未干燥彻底的皮肤提早剥落，这样会刺激皮肤下的柔嫩肌肤。洗澡时用补水的沐浴露，记住，不要给晒伤处脱毛或</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">刮毛哦。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phppka07u\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789d42168134.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">5.试试芦荟</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">都知道富含芦荟的保湿霜和乳能有效缓解晒伤问题，不如直接试试芦荟。去市场上买一棵芦荟，摘一片叶子，用手把芦荟汁挤到晒伤部位。冰凉凉的，感觉真的很棒。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpuZRzqo\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789d42f4005c.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">6.远离太阳直晒</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">不要让已经晒伤的皮肤再晒太阳，等到皮肤修复好后再去海边吧。如果必须在太阳底下时，一定要涂抹</span>SPF<span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">指数高的防晒霜，戴上帽子或穿长袖。当然，得根据你晒伤部位做遮阳工作啦。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpclrses\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789d43d97301.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">7.不要用手抓</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">皮肤痒真的很难忍住不去抓，尤其是边脱皮边发痒的时候。但是你得忍住，抓那些还未到剥落程度的死皮，反而会让皮肤更糟糕。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">要想皮肤不被晒伤，不脱皮，最好的办法就是涂防晒霜，在户外多涂，重复涂才是良方。<br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"></span><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"></span></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phptteTUu\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5789d44969aaa.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '11', '0', '0', '1468650584', '1469702763', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('5799ae83a0c63', '用生命撩妹的仲基如何用生命去保湿！', '雅莉', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799ad61011ad.png', 'skin:article:tag:57319f02782b6,skin:article:tag:5722bc5ee0186', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799adba02757.png', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799ada7e4ec2.png', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">“管理皮肤这件事，就跟看书、运动或是享用美食没什么两样。所以，现在就给自己的皮肤一次机会吧。身为一个开始保养皮肤的男人，我愿意和你一起努力。”</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">宋仲基的《美肤男大作战》中曾说“维持皮肤的柔嫩和白净，才是首要的自我管理之一”这样的观念已经有了认同的第一步了。Wuli仲基从小学一年级开始，一\n连当了9年短道速道滑冰选手。因为要在既干燥又冰冷的冰道上长时间运动，如果不仔细把脸洗干净、不妥善好好保养的话，皮肤很快就会完蛋。只要稍微粗心一\n点，整张脸就会因为干燥而龟裂，甚至因冻伤而泛红。因此从那个时候起，就养成了“洗完脸之后就一定要在上面擦一层保湿乳液”的小习惯。当初只不过是不想成\n为“脸皮红红的土气小男孩”，但经过长时间慢慢积累，现在已经足以进入美肤男的行列了。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">好了，接下去就是我们摘选出来的，关于wuli宋仲基如何用生命去保湿的做法！</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpsFhtKk\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799add91223e.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong>1）选择早上用的洗面产品</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">早上洗脸的时候，是不需要使用洗净力非常强的洗面剂来洗脸的，简单地说就是在洗过脸之后会让面孔“绷”得很紧的那些洗面剂。如果是干性皮肤，那么比起泡沫型，我比较倾向推荐凝胶型洗面剂。冲洗的时候一定要用问谁，要仔细冲洗到泡沫完全冲干净为止。然后，再用冷水冲洗一次。这样可以把洗脸时扩张的毛孔收缩回来，而且可以增加皮肤的弹性，同时延缓水份蒸发的时间。最后用毛巾轻轻拍打擦干。<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 213);\">要像对待心爱的女朋友脸庞一样轻柔地拍着擦干。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 213);\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpAPTC3v\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799adecf28e1.png\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2）用化妆水安抚你的皮肤吧</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">化妆水具有把洗脸时受到刺激的皮肤舒缓的作用。而且还扮演着把洗脸时没能洗净的污垢与残留在脸上的洗面乳清除掉的功能。同时也会对天然保湿层被清洗掉之后一时干燥的皮肤，提供些许水份。直接用手来擦？当然不可以。因为化妆水的主要目的，并不是为了要提供水份，而是要清除掉仍然残留在脸上的污垢。如果是因为角质而烦恼的皮肤，就更应该使用化妆棉！当你亲眼看到刚洗过的脸上，仍然会有被化妆棉擦掉的污垢之后，今后就在也不会省略化装棉了。如果没有充裕时间，那么用温热的水先把脸上的皮脂洗干净之后，再在化妆棉上沾上化妆水，边擦拭边把残余皮脂清除掉也行。 <br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><img alt=\"/tmp/phpsfnGl8\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799ae49a8b3e.png\" title=\"\"/></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>3）没想到保湿剂那么重要</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">洗过脸之后留在脸上的水份会立即蒸发掉，而在此同时，应该要留在脸上的水份，也会一起蒸发掉。务必要立刻制造保湿膜来防止水份蒸发，而且也要适度地给必要的油分和水份。为了如此而擦的东西，就是保湿剂了。不过，要记得一件事情，没有必要同时使用保湿乳液和乳霜。我们之所以会满面油光，那是因为皮肤里的水份不足，所以才要从深层皮肤里把油脂分泌出来，形成了表面的油脂层。这时，必须用水份来代替油分，泌油问题才能得到解决。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">4）养成日常生活中的美容习惯</span></strong></span></p><ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">香烟，没办法戒掉，就先减量</span></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">多喝点水吧，水水水！</span></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">好的食物，可以创作出健康的皮肤（红色类和绿色类的蔬菜、坚果、小鱼等）</span></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">喝酒时也尽量多喝水，多摄取水果、色拉和豌豆类食物</span></p></li></ol><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpvYMZm6\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799ae638975e.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">5）仲基包里的美容小工具</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">保湿喷雾水／吸油纸／护手霜／护唇膏／小镊子</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">其实，读书时代开始就已经养成了身边随时带着整套的收敛水、乳液以及护手霜。所以不只是这5个，洗面乳和洗发水也都会带在身上。跟我们接触的人就知道，我们不但要熬夜赶戏，而且还不时被拉到偏远地区去过夜，所以我的包包里随时都满满地放着这些东西。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">皮肤保养，是为了提升自我竞争力的许多方法中的一种。只要经过些许的努力，就可以得到意想不到的大成果。而健康的皮肤，也就是善待自己的明证。<br/></span></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1469689475', '1469689475', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('5760f24d4fb69', '痘印分类', '颖儿', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5760f22b6cfd3.png', 'skin:article:tag:5722bc5a2b4b8,skin:article:tag:5722bc5ee0186', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5760f24651bcf.png', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5760f23ab5cdc.jpg', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">痘痕也称痘痕，是因为感染发炎或外力挤压所形成，往往是因为在青春痘发作时没有得到及时适当的治疗，皮肤细胞的发炎反应造成了对皮肤组织的破坏，造成了疤痕的产生。 由于青春痘的种类各式各样，所以青春痘痕的形式也有好多种，而青春痘发作时的发炎反应越严重，皮肤组织也破坏得越厉害；发炎的部位越深，皮肤组织被破坏得 也越深，将来可能留下的痘痕也就越严重。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">痘印的寿命比痘痘的长多了，虽说痘印可以随着皮肤</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">的新陈代谢慢慢变浅、消退，但是，这个过程相当漫长，一般至少需要3-5个月的时间。痘印情况轻的可分为红色痘印和黑色痘印两种，这些痘印是表皮浅层的，随着时间的增长，自然会淡化。根据痘印的性状可以分为四大类：</span></p><p><br/></p><section data-id=\"1872\" class=\"v3editor\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 42, 99); font-size: 13px; line-height: 21.0469px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;▼▼▼</span>\n &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">红色痘印</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">形成原因：因为原本长痘痘处，细胞发炎引起血管扩张。但是痘痘消下去后血管并不会马上缩下去，就形成了一个平平红红的暂时性红斑。一般来说，这种红色痘印半年左右可以消失。</span></p><p><br/></p><section data-id=\"1872\" class=\"v3editor\"><p style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 42, 99); font-size: 13px; line-height: 21.0469px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ▼▼▼</span>\n &nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span><br/></p></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp; 黑色痘印</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">形成原因：痘痘发炎后，皮肤组织周围有色素沉淀，就会使红色痘印颜色直接加深，使长过红痘痘的地方留下黑黑脏脏的颜色，使皮肤暗沉。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">痘印情况重的，是真皮或更为下方的皮下组织受损，所产生的直接后果就是留下了凹或增生性凸疤，几乎是外涂护肤品不能解决的问题了；也有可能本身是瘢痕体质，很小的伤口都有可能留下很明显的疤痕。</span></p><p><br/></p><section data-id=\"1872\" class=\"v3editor\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 42, 99); font-size: 13px; line-height: 21.0469px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; ▼▼▼</span>\n &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">凹洞性痘印</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">这种痘印是比较常见的情况，当痘痘发炎太强伤及真皮的胶原蛋白太多时，因为真皮的塌陷而留下凹洞。而很多青春痘患者喜欢用手去挤痘痘，如果挤的不恰当，会大大增加化脓感染的机会，很容易将小粉刺、小痘痘变成大痘痘，然后留下疤痕。而凹洞一旦产生就不会自动消失。</span></p><p><br/></p><section data-id=\"1872\" class=\"v3editor\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 42, 99); font-size: 13px; line-height: 21.0469px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 42, 99); font-size: 13px; line-height: 21.0469px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ▼▼▼</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">增生性凸疤</span></strong></p></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">这是一种过度肥厚的疤痕, 在长过痘痘的地方留下了明显的红色突起，外观又红又肿，而且更严重的是，它会因为搔抓或外力的刺激而慢慢长大。多发生于一些体质特殊的人群身上，这类人群 由于其皮肤真皮层的纤维母细胞太过活跃，在伤口愈合的过程中过度反应，结果真皮因发炎受伤后不但不是凹下去，反而是凸起来，变成肥厚的皮肤组织增生。</span></p><p><br/></p><section data-id=\"1482\" class=\"v3editor\"><p><img data-width=\"100%\" style=\"height: auto ! important; width: 100%; color: inherit;\" src=\"http://7xl0w2.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/14659815152.png\"/></p></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '7', '0', '0', '1465971277', '1469689103', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('5799a6acf0ba7', '美容风水之“葵花”宝典', '美肤专家惠美', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57999a9002427.png', 'skin:article:tag:5722bc5ee0186', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799a699d0a23.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799a6572c6c4.jpg', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">享受假日春意融融，可曾知晓这1年的1／4已经悄然告别（OMG！）。一切都似温吞水般波澜不惊，你渴求的改变在哪里？要知道保持美丽容颜靠的可不仅仅是瓶瓶罐罐的美容品。<span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">换一个空间场景，对待肌肤身体的心情和习惯会随之发生奇妙改变。“风水”结构同样会波及到美丽与气场。</span>做身心光彩的“强运”美人，现在就让我们向你指点几招。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpnzbXwQ\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799a03b2802f.png\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">irene kim的彩虹色头发成为了新生代的时髦符号</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">总是在洗手间匆匆洗个脸就走了；想要节食却总是半途而废；工作压力导致皮肤问题频出……可能是你的房间让你始终无法平静下来自己注视。改换家具位置、改变床单窗帘的颜色，都会带来意想不到的结果。<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline;\">“风水”并非是没有科学依据的迷信，而是一门调整家居和人体“气脉”的大学问，其背后更蕴含了“重新开始”的心理暗示，</span>像中药般缓慢但持久地发挥积极作用。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpzz5MRa\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799a0ca14aba.png\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">除了大红和粉色外，薄荷色和组合色搭配也是让人感到清新与柔和的代表</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong>开运色——温暖大红&amp;魔力粉红！</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">大红色温暖坚强、而粉红色温柔浪漫。无论是用在脸上的美容品还是放置在屋子里的装饰物，都能给你带来开运作用。粉红色除了传统的“桃花”外，还有“信赖、交往、幸福、温柔”的含义，并能带来人际关系上的拓展、保持年轻、不做作的心态。<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline;\">有意识地使用大红色和粉色系的化妆品或服饰，</span>可以演绎出十足的女人味。特色挑选粉色装饰物，不如将粉色瓶子的化妆品摆放出来。而新款腮红中的浅桃色、樱花色也都能给妆容带来青春、清爽的可爱气质。再加上色调温柔的浅粉色甲油，帮助在办公室也能保持和谐的人际关系。<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline;\">它会时时提醒你，“坚强与温柔”的并存。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpN1yB0e\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799a333b2d89.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">出水芙蓉大浴缸</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">天气热起来，选择淋浴的人也多了起来。但是积聚了一天浊气的你其实需要好好泡个澡。毛孔里的污垢、呼吸道的脏空气还有磕磕碰碰产生的小淤血，都需要一个彻底的排毒过程。浴室的布置一定要清晰有条理，尽量避免东西繁杂和混乱。在装饰颜色上蓝色、绿色和白色都是令人沉静放松的好色调，<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline;\">而包裹身体脸孔的毛巾则最好选纯白色和粉色系，这种类似健康肌肤的颜色会给出不少积极的心理暗示。</span>化妆最好在浴后半小时以上再进行，有利于毛孔自然收缩不被彩妆堵塞，<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline;\">而摆一瓶喷雾型化妆水能及时保湿，并为后续护理整理好肌肤状态。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpmbATTL\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799a0df4219e.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">时尚博客kelly走进衣柜总能获得新生般的能量</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">起居室有大魅力</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">为了让好运、良缘、吉报都能顺利而来，保持玄关的整洁干净就显得格外重要。仅仅将香水放置在此处，就可以营造出一抹华丽，并强调出主人的“女性”身份。<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline;\">出门前拿起瓶子来洒上几滴，也能立刻调整到美丽的心情状态。</span>作为利用率最高的场所、社交指数最高的地方，最需要注意的就是肌肤保湿问题。大家坐得够近，所以干纹无所遁形。<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline;\">而使用化妆水时，切忌小家子气。哪怕是平价货，只要用量够足，</span>用温暖的双手仔细贴紧面部并轻轻拍打，就可以让营养成分渗透到肌肤深处发挥作用。 <br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php5GEAk8\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5799a12eee09f.png\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">拉丁美人伊娃郎格利亚的香闺一角，整齐与女性化是关键</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">睡美人爱卧室</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">洗净铅华后顺利地进入梦乡，睡饱美容觉的确是千金难买。想要快快入眠，首先要做好卧房里的准备。将灯光调暗，如果开空调就请将温度调至22℃-24℃。将宠物、手机、电脑请出去，以此保证睡眠质量。<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline;\">花在睡前功夫的时间长短，也是决定变美的关键所在。</span>睡前涂抹可以陪伴过夜的睡眠性美容面霜可以说是一个超级省心的选择。和织物型面膜相比，不必再看着时钟干等15分钟再睡，它的功效也可以一整晚源源不断地释放出来。加上很多相关产品都添加了有利睡眠的香氛，可谓一举多得。对于护肤而言，等你感到需要护理的时侯其实已经晚了一步。特别是唇部、手部等容易干燥的部位，<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); text-decoration: underline;\">将滋润效果卓越的这些小东西放置在床头柜，方便随时使用，</span>可以让你远离“干物女”的恶名。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">“一屋不扫何以扫天下”，风水开路给你的美丽助力加分，还记得新年许下的愿望吗？Come on,baby,Let’s go！</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '3', '0', '0', '1469687468', '1469688918', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('57610ae060b70', '薰衣草精油去痘印', '', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57610aa0e6d23.png', 'skin:article:tag:5722bc5a2b4b8,skin:article:tag:5722bc5ee0186,skin:article:tag:5722bc6d2c46e', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57610ace38c61.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57610ac852899.png', '<p>薰衣草精油是由许多不同类型的芳香族化合物组成的复杂混合物，通过C-ＮＭＲ研究了商品薰衣草精油中的萜类化合物,精油的主要成分芳樟醇、乙酸芳樟酯、薰衣草醇、乙酸薰衣草酯、对-1-孟烯-4-醇、松油醇、石竹烯与别罗勒烯。含少量1,8-桉叶素和樟脑。</p><p><br/></p><p>芳樟醇是薰衣草精油抗菌的主要成分，它能抑制17种细菌（包括革兰阳性菌和革兰阴性菌）、10种真菌的生长。薰衣草醇、乙酸芳樟酯起到芳香剂的作用，能令人心情愉快。对-1-孟烯-4-醇具有杀菌、消炎、消毒的作用。樟脑具有消肿止痛、杀菌止痒的功效。</p><p><br/></p><p>科学黄金比例调配的薰衣草精油，具有极佳的修复功效，消灭痘痘同时快速淡化表皮痘印、痘疤、痘坑，抑制痘痘细菌再次滋生，持久维持无痘无印健康肌肤。</p><p><br/></p><p>使用方法：</p><p><strong>1.按摩法</strong></p><p>取5滴薰衣草精油+10CC基础油，一同稀释混合，涂抹于痘印处，以正确的按摩手法按摩15分钟，可促进细胞再生，使受损组织再生，淡化痘印。</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>2.涂抹法</strong></p><p>将5滴薰衣草精油混合10毫升的基础油一同调配好，洁面后，用棉签沾取涂抹在痘痘痘印处，适合任何肤质。也可涂抹于整个脸部，还可调节皮肤的油脂分泌。</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>3.蒸薰法</strong></p><p>准备香薰炉一台，在盛水器中加入清水，再滴入5-6滴薰衣草精油，然后加热香熏炉，待热力使水中精华油徐徐释放出来，有助于制造不同的气氛。可使体液活动加快，从而改善了内环境，进一步达到调节整个身体的作用。迅速改变局部组织细胞，细胞的生存环境，使其新陈代谢加快。</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>4.吸入法</strong></p><p>在沸腾的热水中加入薰衣草精油滴于热水里，还可配合茶树精油一同使用，但总数不得超过六滴，再搅匀均匀后，再用大浴巾覆盖好，使脸部埋入热水散发的热气中，用口、鼻交替呼吸，维持5-10分钟即可。</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>5.冷敷法</strong></p><p>冷敷的方法跟热敷差不多，只是将热水换成冷水。同样也是刺激皮肤，使皮肤加快新陈代谢，达到快速淡化痘印的效果。</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>6.热敷法</strong></p><p>准备温热水200ml，加入3滴精油，取干净毛巾浸入水中，然后拧干水分。敷在已清洁干净的脸部上，再加以双手轻轻的按压毛巾，使精油快速渗入肌肤，5分钟后取下即可。可加快皮肤血液循环，加快细胞新生，快速去除痘印。</p><p><br/></p>', '74', '1', '0', '1465977568', '1469688786', '5');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('57970e26301af', '陪跑变女主，就是氨基酸', '美肤专家娟子', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579709ace79a5.jpg', 'skin:article:tag:57319e0b05676,skin:article:tag:5722bc5ee0186,skin:article:tag:57319f241d088,skin:article:tag:57319f02782b6', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57970d435d994.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57970d3a70822.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none;\">氨基酸看上去很不起眼，甚至会在各类高大上的成分中被忽略。和各种金光闪闪的美容原料相比，它的存在感真是低到一个新水准。不过别小看它，千年陪跑也有变身女主角的一天（你看，梦想总要有的⋯⋯）</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php5Tkzos\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57970d68c9594.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">作为蛋白质的一部分，氨基酸（Amino）和人体密不可分，比如蛋白质的消化和吸收必须通过它来完成，为健康美丽造福多多。可惜氨基酸种类众多，其中有一大部分无法被人体自体合成，需要从食物或其他补充剂中获得。氨基酸也主持着氮的平衡作用、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">它参与构成多种人体必须营养成分、多用于临床治疗甚至生命急救</span>。当然，它也让我们变得美美的（简直就是美容成分界的老戏骨般地百搭⋯⋯）<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">大约从10年前开始，科学家研发的氨基酸饮料开始风靡东南亚、日韩和中国。有利用丰富氨基酸成分促进多余脂肪燃烧的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: none; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">塑身饮料</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">；也有消除疲劳、增强身体免疫系和快速元气的<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">“加班”饮料</span>，受到潮流人士追捧。当然也有以粉剂、片剂的形式，作为营养补充剂缤纷问世。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php0C5RuV\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57970d8cde299.png\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">（科颜氏的这款氨基酸洗发水口碑好，但价格一直偏高</span>）</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">随着科技发展，氨基酸在大牌护肤品上也逐渐崭露头角，并兵分两路。首先在洁面产品中，启用氨基酸洁面活性剂的洗面产品在清洁肌肤时更温和，彻底清洁同时抵抗自由基，又令角质层保留住更多天然水分，不干涩；<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">继而今年更成为无硅油洗发水浪潮中新的助力。（没错，2015年底开始的洗脑式传播，令洗发水正式进入科技革新台阶）</span>而我们大聊特聊的各种抗衰老“胜肽”，一样少不了氨基酸。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); line-height: 22px; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">氨基酸成分来洗发和洁面，这听上去靠谱吗？</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpa5dlnd\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57970e0e1b1df.jpg\" title=\"\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">事实上：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">（作为表面活性剂，它简直就是满分！）</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">1.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">氨基酸洗发水或洁面乳的弱酸性，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">与皮肤PH值非常亲和</span>，不会导致头屑、头油、瘙痒或过敏的反应。不但成年人适用，孕妇、儿童、老人或过敏体体质人群也都可安心使用，没有后顾之忧。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">2.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">氨基酸起泡剂作为国际上<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">最奢侈（也是最温和）</span>的起泡成份，通常用在高档牙膏中（吞服无害），可以说是配料中的奢侈品。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">3.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">完全的洗护分开，避免头皮或皮肤洗不干净，之后护理又不吸收的两难矛盾。它具有<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">温和又彻底的洗净力</span>，让皮肤头发都能恢复应有的舒畅和美丽。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">4.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">氨基酸表面活性剂主要来自<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">椰子油、棕榈油、小麦蛋白等天然原料</span>。由于配方、生产的成本较高，所以更适合对生活质量有高要求的人群使用。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">5.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">使用时氨基酸表面活性剂的<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">泡沫细腻、绵密</span>，让人感觉被温柔环抱，使用感超好。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">6.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">氨基酸表面活性剂的生物<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">可降解性强，绿色环保</span>，对你好，也对地球好。</span></p><p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 22px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">用氨基酸成分来护肤和抗老，这又行得通不？</span></strong></p><p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 22px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpUqQG2Y\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57970dfc358fd.png\" title=\"\"/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">1.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">氨基酸也常见于</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">爽肤水</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">与</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">乳液</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">中，因为其小分子结构很<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">容易被肌肤吸收</span>，所以被用来扭转干燥多皱、松弛塌陷等衰老现象。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: underline;\">很多品牌主打“胜肽”，其核心成分也就是氨基酸哦！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">2.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">同样适合敏感肌肤。氨基酸本身的亲肤性能帮助提高皮肤免疫功能，增强淋巴系统排毒，提高抗敏性，所以能够<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">温和治愈</span>。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">3.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">氨基酸主要用于修补皮肤胶原肽键和弹力网的断裂，重塑其螺旋网状结构，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">回复青春弹力肌</span>。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">4.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">通过加强保湿来<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">调治肌肤水油不平衡引起的痘痘问题</span>，同时帮助修补痘印改善肤质。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '3', '0', '0', '1469517350', '1469686633', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('575fc825384b7', '痘痘成因', '雨菲', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/575fc804b3a17.png', 'skin:article:tag:5722bc5a2b4b8', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/575fc81df1705.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/575fc810dc939.jpg', '<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\">痘痘，即</span><a href=\"http://www.baike.com/sowiki/所谓青春?prd=content_doc_search\" title=\"所谓青春\" style=\"border: medium none; text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\">所谓青春</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\">痘，又或者叫痤疮、粉刺，是一种毛囊、皮脂腺的慢性炎症，主要发生在颜面及胸背等多脂区。不管是何种类型的痘痘，痘痘产生的根本原因是相同的：油脂分泌过量，毛孔堵塞，细菌滋生，引发皮肤刺激红肿。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">诱发青春痘的原因：</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>1、<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">内分泌失衡</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">人体有内分泌系统，分泌各种激素</span>, <span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">与神经系统一起调节人体的代谢和生理功能。正常情况下各种激素是保持平衡的，如因某种原因使这种平衡打破了（某种激素过多或过少）这就造成内分泌失调，会引起相应的临床表现。痘痘就是内分泌失调的一大表现。因为体内激素分泌不平衡，导致皮脂分泌过多，而过多的油分，没有得到适度清洁的话，残留在毛孔中形成白色油脂粒与皮肤死皮、灰尘等堆积，形成粉刺，使毛孔阻塞毛孔，而堵塞的毛孔一旦发炎就形成了痘痘，如果发生红肿没有得到好好处理的话，很容易留下痘疤。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>2<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、皮脂腺旺盛</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\">皮脂腺旺盛下长的痘痘是因为皮脂堆积导致皮肤呈现油性，皮肤油分分泌过多，堵塞毛孔，因而导致了痘痘的生长。皮脂腺旺盛的这类皮肤就是我们所说的油性皮肤。皮脂腺旺盛跟遗传、生活饮食习惯等因素有关。一般皮脂腺堆积下长的痘痘颜色成暗红色，痘痘成片的生长，不是很大但是数量较多，一般集中在鼻尖两侧和额头上，不会引起疼痛。皮脂腺旺盛的人要特别注重皮肤清洁，运动或外出回家后应该及时洗脸，将脸上的脏尘和油垢洗掉，保持脸部清洁、干爽，避免污物堵塞毛孔。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>3<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、职业因素</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">脸上容易长痘痘跟我们日常所从事的工作也有着紧密的关系。比如高压工作人群，容易因过度压力紧张导致内分泌失调吗，从而引发痘痘；办公室白领，在封闭的工作环境，一天至少八小时对着电脑受辐射，除了上厕所、吃饭，一般都是坐在椅子上，运动量少，体内堵塞堆积，无法排出，痘痘也就容易生长；出租车司机，每天工作</span>10<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">小时，身体长时间靠在坐席上，靠座椅的皮肤由于处于封闭闷热状态，很容易在后背长青春痘。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>4<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、遗传</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\">遗传是痘痘的一大重要因素。一般父母有长痘的历史，孩子也一般会受到遗传。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>5<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、饮食</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">有一些食品很容易诱发痘痘、粉刺，比如甜品、油炸、烧烤、腥、辣味等食物。容易长痘痘的人，最好吃具有清热、解毒、消炎与通便等作用食物</span>,<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">可以帮助预防青春痘和粉刺，比如绿豆、青菜、百合。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>6<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、气候</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\">气候湿热，高温或夏季日晒等，皆会导致青春痘复发及恶化。当气候季节变换，温度骤然升高时，皮脂腺的分泌调节失灵，会造成短暂性的青春痘。如及早处理得当，几天后便会消失。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>7<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、护肤保养品使用不当</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\">护肤品使用不当，主要指没用对适合肌肤的护肤品。比如油性肌肤使用含有分多适合干性肌肤的护肤品，自然就会导致皮肤更油，堵塞毛孔，形成痘痘。购买护肤品时要根据自己皮肤类型进行挑选。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>8<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">、不良的生活方式</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 16px;\">不良饮食习惯、睡眠质量差、长期疲劳、烟酒过量，也是诱使青春痘驻足和复发的慢性原因，伤害力不容忽视。不注意头发，衣领的卫生，习惯于托腮、抠脸等都会成为诱发青春痘形成的外在因素，也是最常见的原因。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '1', '0', '0', '1465894949', '1469686120', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('579721d504ba4', '敏感肌的后裔也有桃花天！', '美肤专家美惠', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57971b4966209.png', 'skin:article:tag:57319ee78836e', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57971ffbc9d34.png', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57971ff13ac92.png', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">温暖的春天到了，阳光下散步、郊游可好？敏感性皮肤的妹子这下又得犯愁，脸脸又要开始泛红、起皮、发痒，出门就红，红的也太不是时机了吧，约个男票介么个“春意盎然”也太不矜持，嘻嘻。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">春天随着气温的升高，花粉、柳絮等高致命物质冲刺整个空间，敏感性的肌肤也容易产生许多不适反应，轻则起皮发痒，重则蹦红血丝或者肿了。那么，敏感肌该如何安然度过春季敏感期呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpvo9UOz\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797200953d47.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">真满想和过敏源好好打一架</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">先说说引起皮肤敏感的原因吧，掐灭敏感源很有必要。</span></strong>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">年龄和生理因素(20%)：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">年龄增长，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">皮肤分</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">泌功能退化，皮肤在岁月的消磨下，会变薄，它的保护层功能亦随之减弱。压力，精神紧张和情绪低落，都会减弱皮肤的天然抵抗力，导致它的自我修护机能亦随之减慢，如内分泌紊乱。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">环境因素(20%)：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">长期暴露在阳光或空气污染的环境中，烟雾，灰屑，紫外光UVA和UVB，以及红外线，均会损害皮肤，因为它们产生的游离子能破坏皮肤的脂质保护层。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">化学和天气因素(15%)：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">一些护肤品中的成分如防腐，染料，乳化剂和香料，都有可能使皮肤变得敏感。劣质化妆品或不当药物伤害。面对天气的转变，肌肤亦需要额外的适应，例如在寒冷天气中，如果皮肤没有充分滋润的话，便很容易受到伤害。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">原因有这些，我们说的春季敏感当让主要指的是天气、环境因素引起的皮肤敏感问题。年龄生理问题引起的敏感咱无法返老还童，不过保持身心愉悦、坚持身体锻炼，增强身体抵抗力还是可以做到的。还是言归正传的说说怎么应对这个既爱有恨的春天吧！</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpZqXW3t\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797218e82977.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">每次一</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">过敏，人也不是很像人了⋯⋯宝宝心里苦</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;远离过敏源</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px;\">（</span>acaai.org建议）</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">a.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;关注天气预报中的花粉和霉菌数量。关闭门窗，开车的记得关好车窗。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">b.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;中午和下午尽量在户内，因为那两个时间段内花粉分子运动最剧烈。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">c.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;户外回来后要洗澡、洗头发、换衣服。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">d.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;长时间在户外的话，需佩戴面罩或者服用抗敏药物。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;饮食清淡，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px;\">尽量避免辛辣油腻食物，鱼腥类海鲜也尽量不要吃，管住嘴。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">减少护肤不当，</span>比如用A酸或果酸浓度过高，时间过长；或是清理角质过度频繁等，先停止这些护肤程序是首要的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">选择适合自己的护肤品。前面说了这么多，其实这才是重点。<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">护肤品的选择一定是越温和越好，成分越简单越好</span>。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpyRNe6x\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579721c09be76.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">哪些成分易引起皮肤过敏？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;香料</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">这7款产品都不含香料，这是有科学道理的。因为二十多年前的一个研究结果的系统总结就指出香料（</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">香氛</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">，香味剂，Fragrance）是引起皮肤过敏的罪魁祸首之一，受试人群中有大约12%的人会有过敏反应。虽然这是以美国佬为对象的实验结果，但是我们完全可以作为参考。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;防腐剂</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">防腐剂是比较容易引起敏感的成分。防腐剂和香料不同，基本上是必须的成分。好在防腐剂引起过敏的几率要比香料小数倍，而且含量一般也少，所以也还好。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体;\">3.<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp; </span>果酸及维他命A酸类成分</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">使用这类产品会有酸性刺激，使用期间会有明显的角质剥落。敏感性肌肤的角质层本身就偏薄，这样自然容易引起过敏现象。因此，使用含有果酸或维他命A酸类产品一定要慎重，或在医生的指导下使用。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体;\">4.<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp; </span>活性成分浓度过高</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">活性成分浓度偏低的产品，引起</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">皮肤</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">不适相对较少，大部分</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">过敏</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">情况都出现在使用了高浓度活性成分产品后，皮肤出现瘙痒、红肿等过敏情况。因此敏感性肌肤在使用一款新产品之前一定要先涂在耳背后做个24小时敏感测试，或是控制使用量，这是使用高浓度护肤品的首要原则。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">护肤的第一步永远是肌肤的健康，然后才是美白、抗老⋯⋯别颠倒主次才好⋯⋯</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 18px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">最后还是提醒大家，无论使用哪种护肤品，尤其是敏感肌的，<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">一定要先在耳朵后面或者膝盖窝窝里抹少量实验一下</span>，一天或者两天没有过敏反应再尝试抹整脸。那些号称纯植物成分的化妆品也应该小心为宜，迷迭香，麝香草，洋甘菊，胡芦巴之类的你生活中没碰过的东西，也许就会引起敏感呢，还是小心为宜。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; text-indent: 32px;\"><br/><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '4', '0', '0', '1469522389', '1469686107', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('578c45f23d285', '用了防晒霜还被晒伤，那是因为你方法不对', '美肤专家慧美', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c428f2e185.png', 'skin:article:tag:5727fef89cb70,skin:article:tag:57319ee78836e', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c44b36b426.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c44a9a55e1.jpg', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">夏天的太阳火辣辣，我们都知道涂防晒霜是不可或缺的护肤步骤。尽管我们去海边时一定不会忘记它，但是在日常护肤时我们还是会犯一些低级的防晒错误。我们通常会认为防晒霜不是每日必需品，只有在关键的时候才需要。并且总是理直气壮，因为只是出门走走，不会在外面待太久；外面是阴天，我们躲在树荫下；温度还不算高，还没达到能灼伤皮肤的程度</span>……<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">虽然我们为自己找到的借口，可是不能阻止太阳干坏事儿。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpsstUgQ\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c456b86dcc.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">在没有任何防护下，阳光中的紫外线会让皮肤更早的老化，长皱纹、晒斑，尽管你的皮肤没有被灼伤。不用防晒霜，受到</span><span style=\"text-decoration: none; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">阳光暴晒</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">时，会增加患皮肤癌的概率。“阳光暴晒”不仅指在万里晴空的烈日下晒太阳，还可以指阴天、冷天情下况持续暴露在阳光下数分钟，不管你是在车里还是在阴凉处。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">UVA可以穿透玻璃，UVA/UVB可以通过水和光进行反射对皮肤造成损伤</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">。</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">所以为了保护皮肤，必须使用合适防晒霜；而且还需避免一些防晒误区。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><span style=\"\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">1.用量不够</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">脸部防晒霜的用量大概为一茶匙，全身用量应为小酒杯的容量。用防晒喷雾时大部分人会偏向于喷少些，西奈山医疗中心皮肤科副教授</span>Dr. Jeannette Graf<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">建议，为了保证喷雾的用量足够，喷洒时瓶身离脸部</span>6<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">英尺，持续喷洒，喷完后揉搓脸部（虽然说明书没那么建议）。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpZorZiA\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c45843e6ad.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">2.没在出门前涂好</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">许多时候我们到了户外才抹防晒霜，这可是不对哦。防晒霜的保护特性需要涂抹15分钟后才能被激发，所以你等到在户外时才涂，皮肤还是受到紫外线的损伤。<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">外出前30分钟就应该涂防晒霜哦</span>。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php1QHcxz\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c45905ed30.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3.穿好衣服后涂抹</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">等到在户外时才涂防晒霜，那证明是你穿好衣服时才涂。我知道很多人怕油腻的防晒霜会把衣服弄脏，所以靠近衣服的部位总是小心翼翼的涂抹。所以身上的小斑点被你遗忘了，皮肤也更容易被晒伤。所以最保险的方法是<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">没穿好衣服时就抹好</span>，全方位防晒。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpUyKh3I\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c459f317b7.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">4.忽视其他身体部位</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">我知道涂防晒霜有点烦人，但你要涂的话干脆就涂个爽快。<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">唇部、耳朵、发际线、手背、手指、脚、肚脐眼</span>，这些部位也给喝点防晒霜吧，虽然他们没那么明显，但也需要保护哒。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpskHMnI\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c45ab7646f.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">5.没有重复涂抹</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">出门别忘记把防晒霜放包里带走，因为你需要重复涂抹。<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">皮肤干燥时，建议每两小时涂抹一次。</span>早晨涂抹的防晒霜到了中午时一般已经失效，需要再次涂抹。如果你下水游泳或流汗多，请读防晒霜瓶身的说明，看防水时效是</span>40-80<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">分钟还是多长，根据说明再进行重复涂抹。</span></span></p><p><img alt=\"/tmp/phpZ1BWzJ\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c45b71978e.jpg\" title=\"\"/></p>', '11', '0', '0', '1468810738', '1469686087', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('57970187cadb4', '埃及艳后Cleopatra的不老秘籍，你不想试试？', '皮肤专家美惠', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5796fcbaa367c.png', 'skin:article:tag:57319f241d088,skin:article:tag:57319f02782b6', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5796ff6e17b15.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5796fea5ef7c5.png', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">我们之前有介绍过羊奶、骆驼奶护肤，今天要介绍驴奶护肤。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">驴奶护肤其实也不是新鲜玩意儿，据说古埃及艳后Cleopatra就用驴奶来保持美丽，每天洗澡的驴奶量就需要700多头驴提供。在20世纪早期，驴奶就开始成为牛奶的替代物之一。最近这些年，有研究称驴奶可以替代牛奶，供给对牛奶蛋白过敏的孩子饮用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">近日驴奶在国外护肤界声名鹊起，因为它对皮肤的确有很多好处，使用效果也显著。在生物化学成分上，驴奶是所有哺乳动物奶中最接近人奶的一种奶。驴奶蕴含酪蛋白、清蛋白、脂肪、乳糖、盐和水。维生素（A, B1, B2, B6, D, C and E：维生素C含量尤其高，能减缓衰老）、矿物质和微量元素（钙、镁、磷、钠、铁、锌）、免疫球蛋白、人体必需脂肪酸和丙三醇烷基的含量非常丰富。因为这些微量元素含量高，所以驴奶的保湿能力、抗衰老作用、皮肤修复、皮肤再生效果都很好。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">驴奶很适合敏感性肌肤使用。敏感肌对许多护肤品会有敏感不适反应，但是实验表明，对驴奶没有过敏反应。驴奶对皮肤有再生作用，因为它的蛋白质、磷脂和天然保湿因子含量高，此外，还能舒缓、重组肌肤。同时，经过验证，驴奶还具有抗皱功效，能去除皱纹，防止脸部、脖子、身体皱纹产生。驴奶脸霜还能紧致肌肤、保持肌肤水分。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不多介绍了，看看有哪些好用，性价比又高的驴奶类的护肤品吧。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1. Cleopatra Donkey Milk Soap <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">驴奶洗脸皂</span></span></strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Cleopatra驴奶皂，具有滋润、活肤功效，是市面上驴奶含量最高的驴奶皂；不含香精、染色剂或任何石油化学成分。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpj6Mx0j\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797013e17483.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2. Donkey Milk Day and NightFacial Cream 驴奶霜日&amp;晚</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这是一款超级滋润的有机面霜，能补充脂肪酸、维生素A、B、C，令肌肤紧致健康，肤色均衡。配方中的非凡抗氧化特性和蛋白质含量，所以这款面霜的抗衰老效果也很不错。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpvoh5L2\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797014f6b0f1.jpg\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">3. Cleomee Donkey Milk Aqua Gorgeous Mask</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Cleomee驴奶面膜具有美白、抗皱功效，能密集滋润、平衡肌肤。含有驴奶和驴油，舒缓、保湿的AQUA专利配方，给肌肤一层保护屏障。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php9mmmiY\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797016de0924.jpg\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">4. Cleomee Snowy Pore Balm</span></strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 34.1333351135254px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Cleomee细致毛孔驴奶膏具有多重功效，既能控油，又能保湿。驴奶和收缩毛孔膏结合，能缩小毛孔、减少皮肤皱纹，提亮肤色，缓解皮肤发红问题，还可以抚平肌肤，均衡肤色。</span></p><p><img alt=\"/tmp/phplESBfU\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797017b8b8c5.jpg\" title=\"\"/></p>', '11', '0', '0', '1469514119', '1469686075', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('5760eef6ce256', '痘痘的部位说明你的身体问题 ', '', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5760ee03d82c7.jpg', 'skin:article:tag:5722bc5a2b4b8,skin:article:tag:5722bc6d2c46e', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5760ee2a5380f.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5760ee0cc8200.png', '<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">引发痘痘的直接原因 是皮肤油水失衡，油多水少，形成毛孔堵塞，导致了细菌 螨虫 毒素 等等在毛孔毛囊发炎，所以我们在护肤上要坚持做好控油、补水、和消炎杀菌 ，这是皮肤上的护理，引发皮肤油水失衡除了皮肤上缺水油多，那么其实也是身体内部的一个反应，所以咱们除了外调，内调也必须做好 这样痘痘才能改善的彻底 ！内调外调缺一不可的。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">一、额头痘VS肝脏</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">如果你的额头总有大粒痘痘不断，那说明你的肝脏已经积累了过多毒素，不规律的生活、昼夜颠倒、长时间熬夜都会让肝脏不能在正常时间（夜里10点～12点）工作，毒素就会积累下来。<br/> <br/> 长效建议：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">让肝脏按时工作(压力大，脾气差，造成心火和血液循环有问题。 应早睡早起，多喝水。) 晚10点按时上床睡觉，让身体进入休眠状态。最晚不能超过11点，躺在床上别玩手机！影响睡眠的，哪怕睡不着，就是放松状态下也有利于肝脏排毒工作。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">二、鼻翼痘VS胃</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">鼻头长痘：胃火过盛，消化系统异常。应少吃冰冷食物 <br/> 当鼻翼处长出痘痘时：除了此处油脂分泌旺盛的原因外，还是胃火过大、消化不良的表现。如果鼻头还有轻微脱皮现象，表明血液循环也不是很好。另外，经常便秘和胃胀气的人也容易长鼻痘。<br/> <br/> 长效建议：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">少食刺激性食品 (与卵巢机能或生殖系统有关。不要过度纵欲或禁欲，多到户外呼吸新鲜空气。)减少肉类摄取，谢绝火锅、冷食和辛辣食品。食物和水都要用温热的，以免刺激胃 液分泌过多导致胃酸，胃酸也会让胃火加剧。一般由于皮脂分泌较多。也可能跟卵巢机能或生殖系统有关。定要及时清除毛孔污垢。另外,不要过度纵欲或禁欲。多 多享受健康自然的环境。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">三、唇周痘VS肠</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">便秘或者肠热、吃了太多辛辣、油炸食物是嘴唇周围长痘的原因，当然，如果使用含氟过多的牙膏也会刺激长痘<br/> <br/> 长效建议：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">舒肠助排毒(便秘导致体内毒素累积，或是使用含氟过量的牙膏。应多吃高纤维的蔬菜水果，调整饮食习惯。 若长在人中部位，则可能是泌尿与生殖系统问题，女性可能会有白带问题，男性则常出现频尿，一定要就医治疗。 ) 服用一次轻泻剂帮助缓解症状，可以配合腹部按摩帮助排出宿便。连吃几天富含纤维的食物疏通肠道，问题就迎刃而解。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">四、印堂痘VS心脏</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">出现在双眉中间的痘痘最不能轻视，回忆一下是否最近经常出现心悸、胸口闷的症状，当心脏活力减弱时这里才会长痘。<br/> <br/> 长效建议：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">注意保护心脏。远离剧烈运动，增加睡眠，远离烟酒和刺激，同时尽快咨询心脏方面的专家，找出问题所在。双眉间长痘，胸闷，心律不整，心悸。建议不要做太过激烈的运动，避免烟、酒、辛辣食品。不要做太过激烈的运动，避免烟、酒、辛辣食品。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">五、发际痘VS毛孔</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">因为卸妆没卸干净，或者清洁时忽略了这个小细节，造成角质太厚，毛孔堵塞，容易在发际或眉间形成细小痘痘。<br/> <br/> 长效建议：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">清洁照顾边缘细节，每天洁面时注意发际边缘的清洁，及时清除会堵塞发际周围毛孔的毛孔代谢物。太阳穴附近出现小粉刺,显示你的饮食中包含了过多的加工食品，造成胆囊阻塞，需要赶紧行体内大扫除</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">六、左脸颊痘VS血液循环</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">左脸颊长痘说明你的血液排毒能力降低，有可能是肝脏出现了问题或是血液循环出现了问题。<br/> <br/> 长效建议：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">加速血液循环 (肝功能不顺畅，有热毒。注意作息正常，保持心情愉快，该吹冷空气就吹，不要让身体处在闷热的环境中。 )不要让身体处在闷热中，可以用温度略低于体温的水洗澡，多到户外活动，吃一些凉血的食物，如丝瓜、冬瓜、柿饼、绿豆等。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">七、右脸颊痘VS肺</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">右脸颊痘痘是肺部有炎症的反映。如果你肺火上升、喉咙干燥、痰多咳嗽，留意一下右脸颊痘痘。<br/> <br/> 长效建议：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">禁食易敏食物 (肺功能失常。 注意保养呼吸道，尽量避免芒果、芋头、海鲜等易过敏的食物。 ) 停止吃海鲜和芒果、酒类食物等易敏食物，过敏会让你的气管、支气管、肺部更加不适。一般表示有肺火蕴热，肺气不宣等的“肺火型”证候。不过这种痘痘多在秋 天出现，而且多会伴有咳嗽、咽痒、咽痛、有痰等症状。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">八、腮边颊痘VS淋巴循环</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">长期肝脏负担加重后，会在耳际、脖子和脸交界处产生痘痘，反复爆发在同一位置，上升为淋巴循环不畅。<br/> <br/> 长效建议：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">促使肝胆排毒。不可劳累，饱饮饱食，适度增加睡眠时间，让大量供应到大脑、肠胃的血液有充分时间供应肝胆排毒。特别要减少睡前饮食的习惯，不加重肠胃负担。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">九、下巴长痘</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">一般表示体内激素失调，周期失衡。这主要是由于体内激素分泌非常旺盛，变化的幅度比较大，内分泌失调而引起的。从现代医学的角度看，青春痘多由雄性激素分泌过盛所致，而女人年过三十，雌激素分泌减少导致对雄激素的制约减弱，造成雄激素相对过盛而起痘。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">长效建议：补充激素。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '26', '0', '0', '1465970422', '1469686067', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('5797130f5bf14', '有的放矢去粉刺，还你无暇肌', '美肤专家美惠子', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579710b64108d.png', 'skin:article:tag:57319eee63041,skin:article:tag:5722bc6d2c46e,skin:article:tag:5722bc5a2b4b8', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57971161abcbe.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579711569c62e.png', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">青春期过了，雨后春笋般</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">涨势的痘痘终于消停，可以仰起脸自信的走路咯。主要矛盾被消除了，次要矛盾已然变成了如今的主要矛盾--粉刺。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">每天很认真洗脸可是粉刺还是不弃不离。于是，看了些资料，编译了这么一篇，供大家参考。（资料主要来自acne.org，nih.gov，familydoctor.org等网站，还有the Journal ofAmerican Academy of Dermatology等学术期刊论文。）</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); line-height: 22.4px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">1.粉刺的前世今生</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpZWXWE4\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57971207580a5.png\" title=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; background-color: white;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">什么是粉刺？首先来看看这两个事实吧，帮你了解什么是粉刺，粉刺为什么去不掉。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">Fact 1:&nbsp;人体有5百万个毛囊，分布在脸部的也有成千上万个。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\">Fact 2：</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\">粉刺就是毛囊堵塞的产物。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">每个毛囊都有一根毛发和一个皮脂腺（生产皮脂让皮肤更加柔软）。皮肤脱落的死皮细胞变会进入毛囊，与油分结合形成堵塞，朝着皮肤表面生长，形成一个小凸起，这就是粉刺。如果小凸起表面的皮肤未变黑，则称为白头粉刺；如果当小凸起周围的毛囊打开，空气进入，使皮脂氧化变黑，黑色粉刺就这么诞生了。如果粉刺发红发炎就行成了我们熟知的痘痘。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">粉刺除了长在T区和下巴，背部、胸部、手臂、肩膀也是他们的福地。粉刺有点像嵌入到皮肤内的灰尘，尤其是黑头粉刺，看着就像没洗干净脸。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">2.导致粉刺的原因</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">1、</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\">粉刺偏爱少年肌</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">身体进入清楚期时，会产生大量的荷尔蒙，荷尔蒙反过来会刺激皮肤油脂腺体。这也意味着粉刺的概率更大，不过这也是百分之百正常，这是身体生长的正常呼唤。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">2、</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\">皮肤清洗不当</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">皮肤死皮会堆积在毛孔内使毛孔堵塞，不及时清洁，堵塞物导致油脂积累。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">3、</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\">使用油性化妆品或护肤品</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">油性的化妆品或护肤品会刺激粉刺的生成。所以应该适合肌肤的产品，使用专门去粉刺的产品。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpb4e7Ah\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797122b3441d.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">一长痘毁所有的心酸，你能体会吗？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">3.哪些护肤品成分能有效对抗粉刺？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">过氧化苯甲酰Benzoyl peroxide</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">和<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">水杨酸salicylic acid</strong>：最普遍最有效的去粉刺成分。这两种成分能杀死细菌、平衡油脂、使皮肤脱皮，可以多种形式出现在胶、乳、霜、肥皂中。不过要看到效果需要大概8周的时间，超过两个月还没效果的话，得咨询下护肤专家咯，看到底是皮肤的问题还是护肤品的问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">当然有些人使用含这些成分的产品后会引起皮肤刺痛、灼热、发红的副作用，这时得赶紧停用哈。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">类维生素A（Retinoids）霜或凝胶</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">类维生素A类，如维甲酸和阿达帕林，可以每天涂一次。使用类维生素A时尽量避免晒太阳，要涂抹防晒霜，因为它会增加皮肤被太阳灼伤的风险。此外孕妇或者备孕期间不能使用他扎罗汀类维生素A，他扎罗汀会导致流产。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">抗生素（Antibiotics）</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">：如果你的粉刺比较严重，医生可能会建议使用抗生素治疗。二甲胺四环素minocycline、强力霉素doxycycline、四环素tetracycline这些抗生素类能减少细菌和防止粉刺发炎，还可以与其他粉刺治疗药如过氧化苯甲酰Benzoyl peroxide结合使用。抗生素可以口服也可以当乳液、凝胶、霜用于外涂，红霉素和克林霉素这两种抗生素就可以用于霜和凝胶中治疗粉刺。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">异维甲酸Isotretinoin</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">：可以用于治疗那种非常糟糕的粉刺咯，不过副作用也是相当的大。使用这类药物时要认真遵照医生的指示。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">避孕药</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">：由于粉刺跟人体荷尔蒙有关，所以女性可以服用避孕药来治粉刺，不过还得咨询医生。男的长粉刺就不要凑热闹吃错药哈。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">4、</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\">环境污染</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">如果您工作或居住的环境中有许多污染物质、湿气、油脂（比如厨房），也会刺激粉刺的产生。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php8fx4Cr\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797124d38232.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">吃太油会长痘？其实未必哦！！</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.有关粉刺的FAQ</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">Q</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">洗脸、搓脸有助于清除粉刺?</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">A</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">脸上的痘痘并不是因为脏东西堵住毛孔造成的，而是毛孔的深处自己闭合而形成的粉刺。清洁过度反而会刺激毛孔，造成毛孔堵塞。毛巾什么的搓脸也会让情况变糟。推荐的最好方式是像猫星人一样用爪子洗脸，一天两次。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">Q</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">压力导致粉刺?</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">A</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">你最好把心思花在找对付粉刺的正确方法上，别纠结老板的催命要求让你爆了一脸痘。压力会影响内分泌，影响荷尔蒙，理论上会让粉刺的情况恶化。但是，有效的对付粉刺的方法完全可以与之对抗。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">Q</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">晒太阳能减少粉刺?</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">A</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">这一条我自己倒是没听说过。不过大家都知道晒多了会损伤皮肤，当下倒不一定怎么样，但是接下来几周却可能因此而爆痘。在抱怨自己被当做狗虐的时候，想想两周前是不是晒多了太阳才导致此轮爆痘吧。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">Q</span></strong></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">粉刺没法根治?</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">A</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">可以。Accutane（维甲酸）就是特效药，三分之二的人群口服Accutane可以根治粉刺。但是，副作用强烈，如果不是粉刺情况特别严重，一般并不推荐。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">Q</span></strong></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">粉刺不能挤？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">A</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">熟了就能挤。那种摸起来疼的没熟，就不要挤（居然有不少人不知道）；没有白头露出来，就不要挤。正确挤法：1. 找根缝衣针就行，用酒精消毒。2. 刺破白头尖尖。3. 用卫生纸裹住食指从痘痘的根部向下挤。4. 挤出血或者透明体液就说明挤过分了。5. 挤不出来不要硬挤，说明还没有熟透，过几天再挤。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">Q</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">用手摸脸会让细菌扩散，导致粉刺？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">A</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(7, 166, 224);\">：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">皮肤表面的细菌并不会导致粉刺，导致粉刺的是毛孔深处的细菌（痤疮杆菌）。用手摸脸可能导致粉刺的真正原因是“摸这个动作会物理刺激皮肤”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p><br/></p>', '2', '0', '0', '1469518607', '1469686015', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('579717e54a72f', '好酒精？坏酒精？皮肤怎么聪明喝一杯', '美肤专家娟子', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797140630d33.jpg', 'skin:article:tag:5722bc6d2c46e,skin:article:tag:57319ee78836e,skin:article:tag:57319eee63041', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579716f774d80.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579716f53bd4a.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em;\">油性皮肤的我每次买护肤品，都有导购热烈建议买含酒精成分的产品，说酒精能去油，能缩小毛孔，真有此效果吗？也有看到美女每次提起护肤品中含有酒精，如临大敌一般，“NO NO NO我不要这个，给我换一个！”酒精到底对皮肤有没有保护作用，在化妆品中又有些什么作用呢？</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">护肤成分中的酒精 Bad vs. Good</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php3jnJdF\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797172dda8b2.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">我们通常所说的护肤品或化妆品中的酒精是指乙醇（ethanol）。成分列表中又名为变性酒精（SD alcohol）、异丙醇（isopropyl alcohol）、变性乙醇（alcohol denat）。这些挥发性醇类酒精能使产品加快干燥，令肌肤感觉轻盈，所以适合油性皮肤的产品中经常能看到这类酒精的身影。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">上面说的几种酒精在化妆品成分表中放在前五的位置，那么这种酒精会引起皮肤刺激，对任何肤质都有害，会导致皮肤紧绷、自由基损伤、降低皮肤修复能力，使皮肤长期处于压力状态。酒精作为护肤品的主要成分是值得我们畏惧的，但不做为主要成分也不是我们想象的那么可怕。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">还有一类名为脂肪醇fatty alcohols的酒精，对皮肤完全没有刺激，例如&nbsp;鲸蜡醇cetyl alcohol，硬脂醇stearyl alcohol，鲸蜡硬脂醇cetearyl alcohol。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">这些成分对干性肌肤有益，如果是少量的话，也适合任何肌肤</span>。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpY56YPK\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797174933954.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none;\">但是！很有必要学会识别有益酒精与有害酒精。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">也许后你会好奇：如果变性酒精类对皮肤有害，为什么好多护肤品公司还使用呢？原因是：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">这些酒精可以保持配方的稳定性或是使厚重的配方用起来更加轻盈，增加使用的愉悦感。这类酒精对产品有好处，但对皮肤无益。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">也许你也听说过酒精是个好东西的说法，因为酒精可以使维生素A和C等成分更好的渗入肌肤。尽管酒精能加强这些成分的吸收，但同时也破坏皮肤屏障。酒精坏处大于好处，其实可以采用更温和的方式使这些成分更好的渗入肌肤。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">酒精是怎样损坏皮肤+令皮肤问题更糟糕？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php9TT9ML\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579717976edb6.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">酒精能迅速损坏皮肤，且在蒸发后会给皮肤带来连锁反应。2003年<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Journal of Hospital Infection</em>曾发表过研究报告，发现经常性的使用含酒精的产品，使皮肤无法阻挡水和清洁剂的渗透，导致皮肤屏障进一步被侵蚀。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">如果你的皮肤是油性的，含酒精的产品对你会更加有吸引力，因为他们能迅速去除油光。但令人讽刺的是，用含酒精的产品去控油，最终导致皮肤更油、毛孔更粗大、炎症更严重，痘印遗留的时间更长。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">总之，酒精会激发毛孔根部油脂的产生，所以快速去油的效果最终反而令皮肤产生更多的油。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">酒精有害，又为何可以用来清理伤口？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpj1F7ex\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579717aa7ba8b.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">现在，大多数医学专家都不用酒精来清理伤口，所以你不必纠结。酒精不仅具有损害性，而且对破开的皮肤也没有消毒作用。<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Dermatology Clinics Journal</em>已经证明酒精对伤口没有消毒作用。尽管酒精有消毒作用，（这也是为什么医生打针前都会用酒精先对皮肤进行消毒），但是对破开的伤口却有害——医生一般用无菌水、生理盐水或碘进行清洗。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;\">最后，总结：</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">1.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">干皮和敏感肌最好谨慎对待酒精。</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">不需要完全避开，而是如果它在成分表中的排名非常靠后的话这样的情况你是可以试一试，觉得没有问题，还是可以买的。但排名在前五的话就要非常慎重了。但最好不要使用含酒精的护肤品。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">2.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">对油皮的建议是，只要不是那种酒精超多的东西，都可以用，但不要长期使用。</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">油皮由于皮脂分泌旺盛，所以天生对酒精的缓冲力较强，但使用酒精后皮脂膜同时也受到损伤，所以还是遵循第一条，成分排名不要靠前，不要长时间持续大面积使用，一周一两次。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">3.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">痘痘肌或皮炎，避免使用。</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">精对破开的皮肤是没有消炎作用的，反而会进一步损伤皮肤屏障，所以为避免刺激，尽量不用含酒精的产品。如果是要进行消炎，还是用替代品吧。</span></p>', '2', '0', '0', '1469519845', '1469685988', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('579728adeef56', '面膜天天见，怎样敷才效果倍儿棒？', '美肤专家美惠', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579725c6562f3.png', 'skin:article:tag:57319f02782b6,skin:article:tag:5779d3841373a,skin:article:tag:57319f12e7462', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797287d12134.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797287330117.jpg', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none;\">面膜是所有护肤程序里见效最快的一道程序，几乎所有有保养意识的女生都会敷面膜，面膜可以提供基础护肤品提供不了的能量，最短的时间内激发肌肤细胞的活力。也有些人在抱怨，天天敷面膜也不见显著效果，那是因为没掌握好敷面膜的方法。今天就来聊聊怎么样才能使面膜发挥最大效果吧。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">敷面膜前要做好皮肤清洁</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">保持皮肤清洁是任何皮肤保养的第一步，敷面膜也不例外。满脸油脂、角质、粉尘，再好的营养也被这些“垃圾”给挡外头。虽然有些面膜使用后需要清洗，但不能两次清洗减少为一次，这可不能偷懒。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">洗完脸后，最好用热毛巾敷脸，坚持几分钟，让毛孔打开，为皮肤大口大口喝营养物质做好准备。其实洗完热水澡敷<span class=\"sys_label_high_light\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">面膜</span>最好，因为这时皮肤上的毛孔充分张开，而且肌肤的水分充足，也可省去专门热水敷脸的步骤（懒人制胜法）。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpCNXToY\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579728bfae2b5.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">Justin Bieber为了格莱美奖闪亮登场，前一天晚上抗衰老祛皱纹面膜赶紧的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">选对合适的面膜很重要</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">不是所有的面膜都适合所有肌肤，也是不是越贵的面膜就越好，不同的皮肤也需要选择不同的面膜。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">干皮：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">保湿面膜</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">干皮嘛，其实做好保湿就好咯，所以面膜很好买，认准基础保湿款。建议</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">早晚各敷一次，然后睡觉时使用保湿睡眠面膜。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">这样即使非常干燥的秋冬季，上妆也不会卡粉了。各大品牌都有保湿，选自己喜欢的就好了。如果需要美白或者抗皱，这种功能性的面膜可以在周三及周日晚上敷。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">敏感肌：舒缓+保湿面膜</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">敏感肌最头疼的问题，就是容易过敏、皮肤敏感易充血，另外季节的变化容易导致肌肤不稳定。因此，能调节肌肤状态的舒缓面膜是首选。另外，由于敏感肌的特性，选择天然有机成分才是上上之选。敏感肌敷面膜就不要太勤了，也不要经常更换面膜种类，带有磨砂去角质的面膜千万不要用。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">建议</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">“</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">舒缓</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">/</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">保湿</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">交替敷，功能性的一周不要超过一次哦。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">油皮：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">控油+保湿+深层清洁面膜</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">最适合大油田的大概还是茶或者薄荷成分的面膜，敷完后脸上肌肤会觉得很清爽。不要因为自己容易出油就觉得不用保湿了，大部分大油田生成的原因其实根本还是在于缺水。另外，过于丰富的油脂分泌也比其他肤质更容易堵塞毛孔，所以请注意深层清洁</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">~</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\">油皮只需保证一周至少四次的保湿即可，其他时候搭配喜欢的功效面膜吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phprqiXue\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57972a0479979.jpg\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll rgb(214, 214, 214);\">面膜还能这么可爱？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(54, 51, 51); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">把握敷面膜的黄金时间</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px;\">究竟面膜是早上做好，还是下午做好，又或者是晚上做最好呢？<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px;\">晚上人体的新陈代谢在夜间处于一天中的低谷，而细胞的生长和修复活动在这个时间中最为旺盛，因而皮肤对营养物质的吸收能力也会有所加强，选择晚上这个时间，加上正确做面膜的步骤，将有助于面膜中的营养成分随新陈代谢传入肌肤底层，从而达到最佳的护肤效果。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px;\">所以通常晚上洗完澡大概九点后就可以开始做面膜了，这个时候皮肤放松毛孔张开，可以较充分的吸收面膜的营养。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpF9EZdr\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57972a128bbb5.png\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 24px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214);\">这自制面膜看着像绿豆汤还是....</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;面膜敷完后做个皮肤按摩</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.1px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 24px; background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\">很多人做完面膜就以为大功告成了，紧接着日常护肤步骤，然后倒头睡个美容觉。其实，去掉面膜后，适当地加以按摩皮肤能使营养液吸收得更好。按摩能给予肌肤适度刺激，提供肌肤内部能量与活氧，血液及淋巴循环变佳后新陈代谢变得正常，同时还可将老废物质排出体外，并且有利于后续保养品的吸收！</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll white;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phplmxRsL\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57973052ab169.png\" title=\"\"/></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '2', '0', '0', '1469524141', '1469606289', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('579707cdd4e84', '为了胶原蛋白，年轻时也该多吃点（你说呢？）', '', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797080d7aca4.png', 'skin:article:tag:57319f241d088,skin:article:tag:5779d3841373a', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797087a34e0a.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579708744eb2e.jpg', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">人体约有10万种蛋白质，我们却往往纠结在占了1／3的胶原蛋白上。 不过胶原蛋白并不单单在脸上，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: pre-wrap; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 31px; text-decoration: underline;\">它同时遍及了身体的各个组织器官，如骨骼、软骨、韧带、更占了皮肤的70％，</span>通过不同的方法，“刺激”胶原蛋白来调整肌肤纹理、弹性、光泽度，已然成为了美容界的必然趋势。换言之，有胶原你就有年轻！</span></p><p><img alt=\"/tmp/phpDx09os\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5797075d6ab22.png\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">(凯特布兰切特和鲁尼玛拉差17岁，胶原蛋白完全不输后辈)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">胶原蛋白是一种细胞外蛋白质，也被誉为“</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\">骨中之骨，肤中之肤，肉中之肉</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">”，是真皮层强有力的后盾，对身体的正常活动至关重要，同时也是使身体保持年轻、防止老化的物质，其对皮肤的作用不言而喻。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">除了对皮肤起支撑作用外，胶原蛋白还起到保湿、滋养、亮肤、紧肤、防皱、修复、营养等作用，能保持角质层水分及纤维结构的完整性，改善皮肤细胞生存环境和促进皮肤组织的新陈代谢，增强血液循环，使肌肤保持年轻。但随着年龄的增长，紫外线的侵害等原因，皮肤内的胶原蛋白含量逐渐减少，逐渐出现了皱纹、皮肤松弛、下垂、甚至还有毛孔粗大、色斑沉淀等等现象。针对胶原蛋白的研究越来越趋于高科技</span>。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php7KAUpL\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579707abbb3d2.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">(詹妮佛劳伦斯也是业界有名的胶原蛋白脸，但她说自己不愿放弃美食，但一定会好好健身以保持好身材)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">1）口服靠谱吗？</span></strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">在日本，很多20岁以上的女性就开始口服胶原蛋白产品。但口服胶原蛋白并非直接转换给皮肤，它会先成为氨基酸被运输到身体需要的部分，在促进身体活化和胶原蛋白再生成。研究结果表明，口服摄入的胶原蛋白，以微小的肽形进入血液，可以使制造胶原蛋白的细胞具有活力。市面上的口服胶原蛋白产品有片剂、饮料和粉末3大类。如果以保证摄入量为前提，粉末是纯度最高、携带最方便的。鱼翅、猪蹄、鸡爪等日常食材中都含有丰富的胶原蛋白，但这些食物分子量大，热量也大，也并非适合每日食用。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: underline;\">日本有很多50岁以上的长辈开始服用胶原蛋白产品来帮助骨骼和关节的健康，没想到吧</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">TIPS：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">1。晚餐中或睡前是最佳服用时间</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">2。配合维生素C服用，可令效果加倍</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">2）涂抹也可行</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">从皮肤外部涂抹方式，获得胶原蛋白可能吗？答案是肯定的。每个人的肌肤深层都是胶原蛋白所存在和活动的地方，表皮肌肤就是最接近胶原蛋白活动区域的地方，而很多高科技的产品，本身就具备良好的被吸收特性,可以通过外部涂抹有效获得胶原蛋白。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">健康年轻的肌肤相对来说就拥有更好的吸收能力，因此同等情况下，能补充到的胶原蛋白也更多。同时，良好的生活习惯也是提高肌肤吸收能力的有效途径，同时推荐使用者注重日常的防晒。当然正确的按摩手法也可以帮助肌肤的吸收。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php21C8C7\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579707bcb9e9a.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">(维密宝贝米兰达可尔是有名的娃娃脸超模，尽管她坦诚也会在社交网站玩玩修图美拍，但脸上的小肉肉可是个人标志绝不会动。)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">3）激光力量大</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">激光作用于皮肤后产生的光化学作用，使真皮层的胶原纤维和弹力纤维内部产生分子结构的化学变化，恢复原有弹性。另外，其所产生的光热作用，可增强血管功能，使循环改善，从而达到消除皱纹，缩小毛孔的治疗效果。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">一般经过一个疗程后，组织切片显示，除了表皮层迅速增厚，真皮层内乳突下方的弹性组织的位置也大量的有新的胶原蛋白生成，在医学角度上证实，可以使真皮层增厚，幼纹、皱纹减少。</span>目前对于刺激胶原蛋白产生安全、舒适而疗效较好的方法有：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">1。Aramis1540nm激光治疗（以激光光波深入皮肤真皮层，活化纤维母细胞以增生骨胶原，重整皮肤底层结构以回复承托力及弹性）</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">2。RF射频治疗（利用高射频频率活化肌底层生产骨胶原的纤维母细胞，活跃细胞令肌肤增生骨胶原,从而抚平皱纹、提升面型轮廓，又能改善肌肤质素。）</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">3。ACR（让自体的生长因子诱导皮肤干细胞分裂出所需细胞，有效修补衰老受损及变薄的肌肤、改善新陈代谢及促进胶原增生，从根源解决暗哑、皱纹、松弛等肌肤老化问题）</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">4）注射最快速</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">针对皮肤老化的部位，人们通过注射的方法给真皮层补充胶原蛋白，以达到支撑真皮组织、恢复肌肤活力的目的。注射胶原蛋白可以治疗脸部的皱纹、凹陷疤痕等皮肤缺陷，这一点和玻尿酸很相像。它们两个都可以用作滋润肌肤、消除皱纹，不同的是，胶原蛋白广泛用于填充比较细小的皱纹、凹陷疤痕和较小的软组织缺损（不会产生后者的透明感）。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">注射胶原蛋白效果立竿见影，但是会被人体逐渐吸收，因此<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">其功效只能维持半年至一年，需要重复注射。</span>注射胶原蛋白时对操作人员的手法有很高要求，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">务必到国家卫生部批准的专业的医疗机构</span>，胶原蛋白注射不均匀时不必惊慌，只需待其吸收，不要做理疗、按摩等操作。患者在注射后短期内不宜做面膜，不要吃海鲜和辛辣的东西，也不能喝酒。个别有瘙痒感，不要挤压、抓挠。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/php6tXOK0\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579707c94fce3.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">（一直被认为是小胖妞的凯特维斯莱特，成年后虽然依旧丰满，但夺影后、拿代言长盛不衰，年轻时的胶原蛋白简直就是一笔财富）</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(214, 214, 214); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: underline;\">唉，说了那么多和主题有关系吗？其实这里的1、2、3、4都可以按照自己的个体需要和经济预算来搭配参考。而吃好每一餐不随意折腾节食减肥才好。因为天生的胶原蛋白永远效果最自然和“免费”！</span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1469515725', '1469516123', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('578c4b43e3516', '毛孔清洁不堵塞，五大方法免费赠送！', '美肤专家丽琴', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c4ac5614e7.jpg', 'skin:article:tag:57319eee63041,skin:article:tag:5779d3841373a', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c4b3927c9c.jpg', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/578c4af32ca72.jpg', '<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">黑头是暴露于皮肤表面的粉刺，黑黑的小颗粒，令皮肤看起来既不干净又不光滑。洗脸有时需要更花心思来清洁毛孔哦。那些用来对付痘痘的洗面奶、爽肤水及局部治疗方法，对于黑头堵塞的毛孔作用甚微。痘痘通过安全卫生的方法挤破后，通常会自然愈合。但是，调皮的黑头总是喜欢证明自己的存在感，就像打不死的小强，所以即使毛孔清洁后，还需要采用合适、规律的方法来保证黑头越来越小，直至消失，不反复出现。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">有什么方法消除这些顽固黑头吗？如果你实在为黑头烦恼，却又不知道自己的方法对不对，可以请教皮肤医生给你建议。你喜欢用化妆品店买的护肤品或</span>DIY<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">的话，其实会发现很多很多去黑头的方法。下面就介绍五个去除黑头、舒缓堵塞肌肤的技巧吧！</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1.蒸脸</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">不管你是想温和的治黑头，还是想为下一段护肤打基础，蒸脸都是一个很好的选择。在盆里倒好热水，把脸放在脸盆的正上方，这样蒸汽就可以帮你打开毛孔。在水里滴几滴茶油或放一片蒸汽丸，再用毛巾从头盖到脸盆，让蒸汽集中于脸部，这样效果会更好。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2.去粉刺工具</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">看到冒出的黑头，我们总是爱去挤或扣，记住千万别用手。用指甲或指尖去挤，会损坏皮肤细胞，导致疤痕。建议使用专业的去粉刺工具。洗完热水藻或蒸脸后，再用工具挤压，更容易去除毛孔中的黑头。不过，你担心用力过度破坏皮肤的话，可以去找专业的皮肤科医生或美容院挑黑头。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">3.鼻贴</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">鼻贴是去除鼻部或下巴黑头的传统方法。你想喜欢DIY的话，推荐你这么做：打开一个棉花球，放入蛋白中浸透；再把棉花球放到有黑头的部位，等到干燥之后再撕掉。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">4.去死皮面膜</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">去死皮面膜跟鼻贴原理一样，只不过是可以方便使用于全脸。去死皮面膜含有抗氧化成分，对皮肤好处多多。闲暇有空的话可以在家自制面膜哦。原料很简单，蜂蜜和纯牛奶。方法也不复杂，把这两个材料混合放入微波炉中热10-15分钟，待冷却后涂到脸部，不过得30分钟后才可以去掉，时间稍微有那么点长。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">5.凡士林膏</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\">充分利用家里的物品，准备好凡士林膏、保鲜膜、毛巾和化妆棉。先洗个热水澡或者蒸脸，把毛孔打开。接着在脸上涂凡士林膏，再用保鲜膜蒙住，然后用热毛巾敷到保鲜膜上面，帮助毛孔充分打开。五分钟后再揭开，擦掉多余的凡士林膏，化妆棉绕着手指缠绕，然后轻轻挤压黑头。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em;\">记住哦，每周或每两周要处理一次黑头，这样才能让毛孔清洁通透。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '3', '0', '0', '1468812099', '1469513637', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('579041d78ff0e', '正确洗脸，避免9大误区', '美肤专家慧美', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5790407c372b2.jpg', 'skin:article:tag:5722bc5a2b4b8,skin:article:tag:57319eee63041,skin:article:tag:5722bc6d2c46e', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/579041a1c3f8d.png', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5790419caee47.png', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">洗脸也有三部曲：打开水龙头，涂上洗面奶，冲洗。不过正确恰当的洗脸远不止这三步骤。首先你得从海量的护肤品中选择适合你的洗面奶、去角质产品、保湿产品。你还得知道哪些洗脸方式对皮肤有益，哪些有害？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">美国皮肤科医生Dr.Jessica Weiser专门从事医药、外科、美容，对去角质、修复成分、皮肤类型及适合他们的清洗方法都有科学专业的见地。所以想好好洗脸，那就听听专家的建议吧！<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">1</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"> 粗糙的磨砂让肌肤更糟糕</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">多度的去死皮会对皮肤有害。“合理地去死皮能防止毛孔堵塞，促进皮肤更新、循环，过度的去死皮会去除那些还未成熟的细胞，刺激皮肤，导致发炎、红肿、长痘痘。”使用温和的磨砂，如Bee Naturals Soft Face Scrub,不含粗糙的磨砂珠子和脱皮成分，采用温和的配方，混合燕麦片、薰衣草花蕾粉、高岭土，轻柔去死皮的同时还能滋润肌肤；质地柔软，不含化学成分、防腐剂、非天然成分。每周轻柔去角质就选它吧！</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpM12kFz\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57903f0c8bba1.jpg\" title=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">2. 挑选适合肌肤类型的护肤品</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"> &nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">“干燥又敏感的肌肤，每天睡觉前洗一次脸就够了”。 Dr. Weiser推荐La Roche-Posay的抗敏感泡沫洁面奶。这款面膜非常适合敏感肌肤，无香精、无防腐剂、经过敏感测试，全世界的皮肤科医生的都建议它；泡沫细腻，持续时间短，易清洗。用户评价说这是他们用过的最好的产品之一。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpXMq6BB\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57903f2f3c824.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">3. 不要用化学成分清洁肌肤</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">“卸妆水是另一个皮肤清洁良方。小油滴可以清除死皮碎片、彩妆、多余油分，而且皮肤清洁后会保持柔软、水嫩，不脱皮“。inVitamin的卸妆水不含化学成分、酒精、起泡剂，含有微胶粒——亲油亲水的微分子团，能吸附在多余的污垢、彩妆、杂质上，把他们从毛孔中带走，但不会破坏皮肤自然平衡。尤能是能有效对付顽固的化妆品，如防水的睫毛膏或粉底。不含添加剂，适用于所有肌肤，干性肌肤、痘痘肌等，都可放心使用。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"m