62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">“蜂蜜具有修复伤口、抗菌、抗炎特性”,Bee Friendly的有机蜂蜜洁面奶含有天然纯正的夏威夷野花蜂蜜，及许多天然成分，如榛子、芦荟 、甜柑橘油、天竺葵。如果你是油性肌肤，建议你试试Bee Friendly的洁面奶吧。这款洗面奶泡沫丰富，洗净力强，能保湿，洗后没有紧绷感；因为蜂蜜天然抗菌，所以还能减少痘痘。用过的人都会点赞，你也来点赞吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpx09fcp\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57903fa7f3fac.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">7. </span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">皮肤容易缺水，请用玻尿酸</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">“尿酸能给表皮制造一个保湿屏障，吸收一千倍自己体重的水分让缺水的肌肤得到恢复”，Amara Organics的玻尿酸精华会给干燥或疲劳的肌肤带来神奇的效果。Amara Organics的玻尿酸取自印度番泻种子，不含防腐剂、酒精；还含有其他滋润成分，如榛子、维生素E、C。用户评价说吸收快、不油腻，用后皮肤水嫩，饱满，有光泽。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"></span></p><img alt=\"/tmp/phpsytMWN\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/57903fcdac0c1.png\" title=\"\"/><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">8. 不要让干燥的肌肤受损伤，使用天然油脂</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">“护肤最重要的一个方面是：清洁皮肤后，能保持皮肤的天然油分”。神经酰胺能帮助表皮形成一个天然屏障。大麻子油含有这种神经酰胺。Herbal Choice的有机亚麻籽油100%纯天然，经过美国农业部USDA有机认证。亚麻籽油不仅能平衡油性肌肤，改善痘痘，还具有保护特性。因为神经酰胺能保留肌肤天然水分，防止肌肤受到化学物质及环境刺激。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phplKQsNt\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5790401508890.png\" title=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">9. 不要用海绵或洗脸刷，用更柔软的吧</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\">“海绵或洗脸刷不适合用于当做日常洗脸工具”。过度使用洗脸刷会导致皮肤过度摩擦，带来损伤。Dr. Weiser建议使用柔软的毛巾洗脸。Bamboo Baby的洗脸巾在护肤界可谓横扫千军，人们对它的温柔赞不绝口。Bamboo Baby的毛巾由耐用、环保的竹子制成，比棉制的毛巾更柔软、更卫生，因为竹子具有抗菌特性。这款毛巾属于低敏性质，适合敏感肌肤，100%可机洗，尺寸大小适中。尽管它很柔软很适合新生儿使用，但是很多人却占为己有哦。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box ! important; word-wrap: break-word ! important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体,SimSun;\"><img alt=\"/tmp/phpHZc4xl\" src=\"http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5790403626b34.png\" title=\"\"/><br/></span></p>', '6', '0', '0', '1469071831', '1469505658', '0');
INSERT INTO `encyclopedia` VALUES ('5760f3d42a7fe', '哪些护肤成分能有效抗痘？', '', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5760f32a663fe.jpg', 'skin:article:tag:5722bc5a2b4b8,skin:article:tag:5722bc6d2c46e,skin:article:tag:57319eee63041', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5760f3a7e72cb.png', 'http://oss-qiwo-dev.qiwocloud1.com/skin/5760f399cb1f0.png', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">痘痘主要因为皮脂分泌过多、毛囊堵塞，导致皮肤受细菌感染，引发炎症。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">痘痘不严重的情况下，可以通过日常护理得到调理改善。而比较严重的痘痘需要到专业医院的皮肤科进行治疗。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">我们在这主要针对痘痘的日常护理。由于痘痘机主要因为皮脂分泌过多而诱发，所以日常护理中只有对皮肤表面及皮脂腺进行针对性的改善，规律肌肤油脂分泌，才能从根本上解决问题，使油脂分泌恢复正常规律，令痘痘消失。日常护理中要从深度清洁、抑制细菌滋生、调节水油平衡、舒缓镇定肌肤这几个方面出发，解决皮肤油脂分泌问题。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">洗面奶选用去油性较强的产品。每天早晚用温水洗脸，能够更彻底的溶解油分，洗脸次数不超过三次。要定期去角质，去除死皮，防止老废角质堆积堵塞毛孔。一般油性肌肤一周去一次角质，干性肌肤半个月一次，敏感性肌肤不建议去角质。保湿产品应用清爽型，忌用含油脂类成分多的产品。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">护肤成分的选择上，应选用具有控油、消炎杀菌、清洁毛孔效果的成分。下面介绍一些祛痘成分：</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>茶树油</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">茶树油最突出的功效就是消炎，杀菌，平衡油脂，尤其是对那些已经有脓的痘痘或者是红肿发炎的暗疮。茶树精油直接涂抹在脓肿的痘痘上，一般一到两天的样子，红肿痘痘就会“干瘪”了。只不过茶树精油一般具有感光性，因此一般要在夜间使用。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>水杨酸类</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">油脂调理因子水杨酸类能有效清除皮肤表面的油光和杂质，缓解皮肤发红症状，让肌肤显得比较清爽。是一种针对皮脂腺进行作用的方式来预防痘痘的发生。这种成分有一定的刺激性，适合中性、油性及混合性肌肤，不适合敏感肌肤。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>过氧化苯甲酰</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">过氧化苯甲酰是最广泛的治疗方法之一，它可以释放皮肤深层的氧气。堵塞的毛孔为细菌的生长创造了一个良好环境，而过氧化苯甲酰通过释放氧气，让细菌缺氧，从而达到阻止细菌生长，杀死细菌的目的。持续使用过氧化苯甲酰可以有效遏制粉刺爆发。使用后可能引起轻微干燥及脱皮，敏感及干性肌肤需提前试用。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>金缕梅</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">金缕梅对於油性肌肤或是过敏的肌肤都有很优异的效果。同时金缕梅能收敛毛孔、补湿、静肌作用；作更深层的洁净，使皮肤更加幼滑亮丽，而且它能迅速渗入皮肤，由内而外全面调节肌肤；平衡皮肤PH值及油脂分泌，净化毛孔；修复受损的肌肤，有效调节舒张的毛孔，明显收敛粗毛孔，防止黑头、粉刺产生，使肌肤快速呈现细腻、光滑、紧致状态。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>薰衣草精华</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">薰衣草精油在清热解毒，清洁皮肤，控制油分，修复肌肤上有很好的效果。薰衣草精油能迅速进入毛囊，清除毛囊内堆积物，疏通毛孔清除多余油脂；深层调节皮肤PH值，控制表皮肌肤油脂分泌，恢复肌肤水油平衡的最佳状态；具有极佳的修复功效，消灭痘痘同时快速淡化表皮痘印、痘疤、痘坑，抑制痘痘细菌再次滋生。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>维生素A酸</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">维生A酸的主要功能为去角质，能脱除过厚的角质，侵入毛囊壁溶解角化层。但是使用维A酸可能会导致干燥问题，因此不建议长期大面积使用，适合有光敏感性，不可于白天使用。干燥、敏感肌肤要谨慎选择。使用维生素A酸的浓度不宜过高，一般非处方的产品 有5%和10%的浓度。外用的产品涂在皮肤上要避免阳光，因为维生素A是光敏感的物质，涂上暴晒反而刺激皮肤。同时维生素A酸也是极为有名的抗氧化成分， 能够改善皮肤老化所引起的皱纹及粗糙。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '8', '1', '0', '1465971668', '1468931249', '0');
